# i18n rules

Read AGENTS.md "Internationalisation" section for full architecture before editing these files.

## Translations

- Add keys to **all four** locale files (en, es, fr, ar) simultaneously.
- Use `useTranslation()` hook — never hard-code English in JSX.
- For sentences with inline links: use prefix/linkText/suffix key pattern (see `contact.para1Prefix` / `contact.applyLinkText` / `contact.para1Suffix`).
- Do not translate proper nouns: HAR.com, RFTA, W-2, 1099, SSN, VA, SSDI, SSA/SSI, Section 8, TCDRS, TRS, FERS, dog breed names.

## Provider architecture

- Provider order in `index.jsx`: `LanguageProvider` → `ThemeModeProvider` → app. Reversing breaks the RTL Emotion cache.
- `ThemeModeProvider` reads `isRTL` internally from `useLanguage()` — do not pass as prop.

## RTL layout

- JS inline styles: `marginInlineEnd` / `marginInlineStart`, not `marginRight` / `marginLeft`.
- Styled-components CSS: `margin-inline-end`, not `margin-right`.
- MUI `direction: 'rtl'` flips most spacing — verify Drawer anchor, icon placement, flex direction.
- Arabic font stack is set via `[dir="rtl"] body` in `index.css` — do not override inline.
